data.description: Private oasis in your own backyard! Fully fenced and treelined by Green Giants, Burning Bushes and Crepe Myrtles. Inground pool 2015. Large Pool House has plenty of storage room and a garage door. Tiki Bar, deck, and hot tub Wow! Enjoy views of fall foliage and spacious neighborhood from your covered front porch. No HOA. Kitchen boasts granite countertops, breakfast nook, under bar seating, pantry and Refrigerator is included. Separate Laundry Room with shelving-Washer/Dryer stays. Spacious Master Bath has separate shower, double vanities and jetted tub. Large walk-in closets. Enjoy Open Floor Plan in Great Room with woodburning fireplace. Floored attic in garage. Luxury Vinyl waterproof flooring, paint, dishwasher - 2 years old. 24 miles to Nashville. All Brick Home shows real pride of ownership! Veterans: ask me about VA loan assumability at 2.75%
